*speex-1.1.12 (18 Apr 2006)

  18 Apr 2006; Patrick McLean <chutzpah@gentoo.org> +speex-1.1.12.ebuild,
  -speex-1.1.5.ebuild:
  Version bump, added vorbis-psy USE flag for new support for vorbis-style
  psychoacoustics (bug 130197), Clean up an old version.

  07 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  speex-1.1.5.ebuild, speex-1.1.7.ebuild:
  Drop virtual/libc dependency.

  16 Jan 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +speex-1.1.5.ebuild:
  Re-add speex 1.1.5 that I forgot to ignore when removing old versions, sorry.

  15 Jan 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -files/speex-1.1.10-sse.patch, -speex-1.0.2.ebuild, -speex-1.0.3.ebuild,
