*speex-1.0_beta3 (12 Nov 2002)

  15 nov 2002; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> speex-1.0_beta3.ebuild :
  Added ppc

  12 Nov 2002; Matt Keadle <mkeadle@gentoo.org> speex-1.0_beta3.ebuild
  files/digest-speex-1.0_beta3

  The most obvious change is going from 'Speex' to 'speex'. This is heading to
  portage unmasked as there are a few things wanting to depend on it. Has been
  very stable on four test machines here.

  This is an extention of the ChangeLog for 'Speex', so that its previous
  records can still be available.

